classifiers: License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License (GPL)
info.description:
A graphical univariate and multivariate analysis package for WinXP and Linux.
Features ANOVA & Kruskal-Wallis tests, principal components analysis (PCA),
discriminant function analysis (DFA), cluster analysis, partial least squares DA
and regression, genetic algorithms for feature selection.
info.name: PyChem
info.summary: A platform-independent graphical environment for multivariate analysis incorporating a number of categorical and quanitative multivariate modelling routines
